  "title": "Store Supervisor #JTL",
  "description": "<ul><li>Boxing and unboxing of parts from and for shipments.</li><li>Perform physical counts of inventories and prepare them for issuance to operations. </li><li>Move parts to designated locations in the factory using pallet truck. </li><li>Loading and unloading from and to lorry production parts and raw materials. </li></ul><p><strong>Requirements </strong><br /></p><ul><li>Preferably having a minimum of 2 years working experiences.</li><li>Computer literate and familiar with ERP system or other forwarders or suppliers portal. </li><li>Preferably with a valid Forklift Driving License. </li></ul><p><strong>Interested candidates please send in your resume to:</strong><br /><strong>Topaz Liang Huimin (CEI No. R1104500), email to: topaz@recruitexpress.com.sg </strong><br /><strong>EA License No. 99C4599</strong></p>",
